body:
### Welcome benjaminDev

This is a collection of my work and side projects. Unfortunately most is still private. I hope to do work that is open but as of now that is how it is.

I'm currently doing my MSc at the University of Cape Town. Some of my results can be seen [here](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UMq8xxmfccs) more to come in October...

My interests are in:
* Image Processing
* Digital Signal Processing
* Radar
* Anything Software related
* Visualizations
* Outdoor activities: Rock climbing, mountain biking, surfing.


Skill Set:
* C++, Python, C#, Matlab
* TDD (gtest), Git
